action.prompt:
Research the following topic comprehensively:

**Topic:** {{topic | text:placeholder="Enter research topic":required}}

**Focus Areas:** {{focus | textarea:placeholder="Specific aspects to focus on..."}}

**Depth:** {{depth | select:options=["Quick Overview","Standard Analysis","Deep Dive"]:default="Standard Analysis"}}

Please provide well-sourced information with citations.

Generate an image with the following specifications:

**Description:** {{description | textarea:placeholder="Describe the image you want to create...":required}}

**Style:** {{style | select:options=["Photorealistic","Digital Art","Oil Painting","Watercolor","Sketch","Anime","3D Render","Minimalist","Abstract"]:default="Photorealistic"}}

**Mood:** {{mood | select:options=["Bright & Cheerful","Dark & Moody","Calm & Serene","Dramatic","Whimsical","Professional"]:default="Bright & Cheerful"}}

**Aspect Ratio:** {{aspect | select:options=["Square (1:1)","Landscape (16:9)","Portrait (9:16)","Wide (21:9)"]:default="Square (1:1)"}}

Design a logo with these specifications:

**Brand/Company Name:** {{name | text:placeholder="Brand name":required}}

**Industry:** {{industry | text:placeholder="e.g., Technology, Food, Fashion"}}

**Style:** {{style | select:options=["Modern & Minimal","Classic & Elegant","Bold & Dynamic","Playful & Fun","Tech & Futuristic","Natural & Organic"]:default="Modern & Minimal"}}

**Colors:** {{colors | text:placeholder="Preferred colors (e.g., blue and white)"}}

**Include Icon:** {{include_icon | checkbox:default=true}} Include a symbol/icon with the text

**Additional Notes:** {{notes | textarea:placeholder="Any specific elements or references..."}}

Write a {{tone | select:options=["Professional","Friendly","Formal","Casual"]:default="Professional"}} email to {{recipient | text:placeholder="Recipient name":required}} about {{subject | text:placeholder="Email subject":required}}.

Key points to include:
{{points | textarea:placeholder="List the main points to cover..."}}

{{include_signature | checkbox:default=true}} Include a professional signature for {{USER_NAME}}

Create structured meeting notes:

**Meeting Title:** {{title | text:placeholder="Meeting name":required}}
**Date:** {{date | date:required}}
**Attendees:** {{attendees | textarea:placeholder="List attendees..."}}

**Discussion Topics/Transcript:**
{{topics | textarea:placeholder="Paste transcript or key discussion points...":required}}

Please provide:
1. Executive summary
2. Key decisions made
3. Action items with owners
4. Next steps

Review this contract and provide analysis:

**Contract Type:** {{type | select:options=["NDA","Service Agreement","Employment","Lease","Purchase Agreement","Partnership","Other"]:required}}

**Contract Text:**
{{contract | textarea:placeholder="Paste contract text...":required}}

**Focus Areas:** {{focus | select:options=["Key Terms","Risk Analysis","Compliance","Negotiation Points","Full Review"]:default="Full Review"}}

Please identify key terms, potential risks, and notable clauses.

Conduct competitor analysis:

**Your Company/Product:** {{company | text:placeholder="Your company":required}}
**Competitor(s):** {{competitors | textarea:placeholder="List competitors to analyze...":required}}
**Industry:** {{industry | text:placeholder="Industry/sector"}}

**Analysis Type:** {{analysis | select:options=["SWOT Analysis","Feature Comparison","Pricing Analysis","Market Position","Full Competitive Review"]:default="Full Competitive Review"}}

Provide detailed competitive intelligence with actionable insights.

Create a presentation outline:

**Topic:** {{topic | text:placeholder="Presentation topic":required}}
**Audience:** {{audience | select:options=["Executive Team","Board of Directors","Clients","Team Members","Investors","Conference"]:required}}
**Duration:** {{duration | select:options=["5 minutes","15 minutes","30 minutes","1 hour"]:default="15 minutes"}}
**Objective:** {{objective | textarea:placeholder="What should the audience take away?"}}

Generate a structured outline with key points and suggested talking points for each slide.

Help me with SQL:

**Database Type:** {{db | select:options=["PostgreSQL","MySQL","SQL Server","SQLite","Oracle","BigQuery"]:default="PostgreSQL"}}

**Task:** {{task | select:options=["Write a new query","Optimize existing query","Debug query","Explain query","Convert between databases"]:required}}

**Table Schema (if known):**
{{schema | textarea:placeholder="Describe your tables and columns..."}}

**Request:**
{{request | textarea:placeholder="Describe what you need...":required}}

Generate a weekly status report:

**Week Ending:** {{week | date:required}}
**Project/Team:** {{project | text:placeholder="Project or team name":required}}

**Accomplishments this week:**
{{accomplishments | textarea:placeholder="List what was completed...":required}}

**In Progress:**
{{in_progress | textarea:placeholder="Current work items..."}}

**Blockers/Risks:**
{{blockers | textarea:placeholder="Any blockers or risks?"}}

**Next Week's Priorities:**
{{next_week | textarea:placeholder="Planned focus areas..."}}

Format as a professional status report suitable for {{audience | select:options=["Manager","Leadership","Stakeholders","Team"]:default="Manager"}}.
